OfficeAlert.Name: Office2013SP1Required
OfficeAlert.Title: Office 2013 (MSI install) users should install Service Pack 1
OfficeAlert.Text: Starting with the April 2015 updates for Office 2013, you will need Office 2013 Service Pack 1 (SP1) installed. Otherwise, you will not be able to install the updates. Click the 'More information' link to access the SP1 download article.
